Package Model

Class Inventory

  • java.lang.Object
    • Model.Inventory
  • public class Inventory
extends java.lang.Object
    Inventory class this class will hold and inventory all the parts and products that currently in the system. This class will have methods that will allow for the addition, deletion and the updating of a part or product that is currently in the lists of parts or products.

      • lookupPart

        public static Part lookupPart​(int partId)
        Method that search(looks-up) the part in the Parts list. This method searches by the part id.

        Receives as a parameter the part as an integer

        Returns a Part object if it is found in the list of parts otherwise a null will be returned.

        Post: The Part has been found or a null value has been returned

        Parameters:
        partId - The part Id
        Returns:
        Part or null

      • lookupProduct

        public static Product lookupProduct​(int productId)
        Method to search(look-up) a Product using the the product Id.

        Receives as an integer parameter the product id.

        Returns a product object if the product is found in the list otherwise it returns null. Signifying that the value is not in the current list of products.

        Post The Product has been found and returned or the value of null has been returned indicating not found.

        Parameters:
        productId - The product Id
        Returns:
        lookupProduct or null

      • deletePart

        public static boolean deletePart​(Part selectedPart)
        Method to delete a part from the allPartsList. It will delete the selected part from the list of allParts.

        Receives a part object to be deleted.

        Returns true if the part has been deleted successfully other wise false if the part was not found in the allParts list.

        Post: The part has been deleted.

        Parameters:
        selectedPart - The Part to be deleted.
        Returns:
        Boolean true if deleted false if was not deleted

      • deleteProduct

        public static boolean deleteProduct​(Product selectedProduct)
        Method to delete a product from the allProduct list. It will delete the selected product from the list of allProducts.

        Receives a Product object to be deleted.

        Returns true if the product has been deleted successfully other wise false if the product was not found in the allProducts list.

        Post: The product has been deleted.

        Parameters:
        selectedProduct - The product to be deleted
        Returns:
        Boolean true for deleted false for not deleted
